#3. Create a 33 matrix B using the following data [14,52,75,89,10,91,51,44,28]. Using matrix A and B find A + B, A - B and AB.

matrix_A= matrix(c(4,5,7,8,0,9,5,4,8), nrow = 3, ncol = 3, byrow = TRUE)
matrix_A
##      [,1] [,2] [,3]

## [3,]    5    4    8

matrix_B
##      [,1] [,2] [,3]
## [1,]   14   52   75
## [2,]   89   10   91
## [3,]   51   44   28

sum
##      [,1] [,2] [,3]

## [2,]   97   10  100
## [3,]   56   48   36
